{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":818,"text":"Once upon a time"},{"time":2328,"text":"we lived in an economy of financial growth and prosperity."},{"time":8979,"text":"This was called the Great Moderation,"},{"time":12674,"text":"the misguided belief by most economists,"},{"time":16080,"text":"policymakers and central banks"},{"time":19383,"text":"that we have transformed into a new world"},{"time":22714,"text":"of never-ending growth and prosperity."},{"time":26571,"text":"This was seen by robust and steady GDP growth,"},{"time":31314,"text":"by low and controlled inflation,"},{"time":34314,"text":"by low unemployment,"},{"time":36553,"text":"and controlled and low financial volatility."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40459,"text":"But the Great Recession in 2007 and 2008,"},{"time":47091,"text":"the great crash, broke this illusion."},{"time":50570,"text":"A few hundred billion dollars of losses in the financial sector"},{"time":55594,"text":"cascaded into five trillion dollars"},{"time":59674,"text":"of losses in world GDP"},{"time":61558,"text":"and almost $30 trillion losses"},{"time":65361,"text":"in the global stock market."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69306,"text":"So the understanding of this Great Recession"},{"time":74501,"text":"was that this was completely surprising,"},{"time":79862,"text":"this came out of the blue,"},{"time":81208,"text":"this was like the wrath of the gods."},{"time":84125,"text":"There was no responsibility."},{"time":85916,"text":"So, as a reflection of this,"},{"time":87839,"text":"we started the Financial Crisis Observatory."},{"time":91448,"text":"We had the goal to diagnose in real time"},{"time":95386,"text":"financial bubbles"},{"time":97757,"text":"and identify in advance their critical time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103614,"text":"What is the underpinning, scientifically, of this financial observatory?"},{"time":106972,"text":"We developed a theory called \"dragon-kings.\""},{"time":111598,"text":"Dragon-kings represent extreme events"},{"time":114804,"text":"which are of a class of their own."},{"time":118076,"text":"They are special. They are outliers."},{"time":120919,"text":"They are generated by specific mechanisms"},{"time":124359,"text":"that may make them predictable,"},{"time":127245,"text":"perhaps controllable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130143,"text":"Consider the financial price time series,"},{"time":133970,"text":"a given stock, your perfect stock,"},{"time":136143,"text":"or a global index."},{"time":138495,"text":"You have these up-and-downs."},{"time":140549,"text":"A very good measure of the risk of this financial market"},{"time":144111,"text":"is the peaks-to-valleys that represent"},{"time":146533,"text":"a worst case scenario"},{"time":148829,"text":"when you bought at the top and sold at the bottom."},{"time":152502,"text":"You can look at the statistics, the frequency of the occurrence"},{"time":156251,"text":"of peak-to-valleys of different sizes,"},{"time":158606,"text":"which is represented in this graph."},{"time":161157,"text":"Now, interestingly, 99 percent"},{"time":164189,"text":"of the peak-to-valleys of different amplitudes"},{"time":167982,"text":"can be represented by a universal power law"},{"time":171442,"text":"represented by this red line here."},{"time":174893,"text":"More interestingly, there are outliers, there are exceptions"},{"time":179039,"text":"which are above this red line,"},{"time":180942,"text":"occur 100 times more frequently, at least,"},{"time":184701,"text":"than the extrapolation would predict them to occur"},{"time":188854,"text":"based on the calibration of the 99 percent remaining"},{"time":192791,"text":"peak-to-valleys."},{"time":195040,"text":"They are due to trenchant dependancies"},{"time":199640,"text":"such that a loss is followed by a loss"},{"time":203152,"text":"which is followed by a loss which is followed by a loss."},{"time":206115,"text":"These kinds of dependencies"},{"time":209226,"text":"are largely missed by standard risk management tools,"},{"time":214838,"text":"which ignore them and see lizards"},{"time":217767,"text":"when they should see dragon-kings."},{"time":221586,"text":"The root mechanism of a dragon-king"},{"time":225503,"text":"is a slow maturation towards instability,"},{"time":228639,"text":"which is the bubble,"},{"time":230261,"text":"and the climax of the bubble is often the crash."},{"time":232891,"text":"This is similar to the slow heating of water"},{"time":236516,"text":"in this test tube reaching the boiling point,"},{"time":239419,"text":"where the instability of the water occurs"},{"time":241909,"text":"and you have the phase transition to vapor."},{"time":245246,"text":"And this process, which is absolutely non-linear --"},{"time":248923,"text":"cannot be predicted by standard techniques --"},{"time":251203,"text":"is the reflection of a collective emergent behavior"},{"time":255379,"text":"which is fundamentally endogenous."},{"time":257758,"text":"So the cause of the crash, the cause of the crisis"},{"time":260971,"text":"has to be found in an inner instability of the system,"},{"time":264155,"text":"and any tiny perturbation will make this instability occur."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270191,"text":"Now, some of you may have come to the mind"},{"time":273891,"text":"that is this not related to the black swan concept"},{"time":276516,"text":"you have heard about frequently?"},{"time":279451,"text":"Remember, black swan is this rare bird"},{"time":281868,"text":"that you see once and suddenly shattered your belief"},{"time":285277,"text":"that all swans should be white,"},{"time":287751,"text":"so it has captured the idea of unpredictability,"},{"time":291295,"text":"unknowability, that the extreme events"},{"time":292804,"text":"are fundamentally unknowable."},{"time":295635,"text":"Nothing can be further"},{"time":297360,"text":"from the dragon-king concept I propose,"},{"time":299998,"text":"which is exactly the opposite, that most extreme events"},{"time":303716,"text":"are actually knowable and predictable."},{"time":306939,"text":"So we can be empowered and take responsibility"},{"time":310444,"text":"and make predictions about them."},{"time":312663,"text":"So let's have my dragon-king burn this black swan concept."}]},{"cues":[{"time":315863,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":317489,"text":"There are many early warning signals"},{"time":320429,"text":"that are predicted by this theory."},{"time":322308,"text":"Let me just focus on one of them:"},{"time":324675,"text":"the super-exponential growth with positive feedback."},{"time":327827,"text":"What does it mean?"},{"time":328987,"text":"Imagine you have an investment"},{"time":331160,"text":"that returns the first year five percent,"},{"time":334314,"text":"the second year 10 percent, the third year 20 percent,"},{"time":337469,"text":"the next year 40 percent. Is that not marvelous?"},{"time":340011,"text":"This is a super-exponential growth."},{"time":343409,"text":"A standard exponential growth corresponds"},{"time":345346,"text":"to a constant growth rate, let's say, of 10 percent"},{"time":349090,"text":"The point is that, many times during bubbles,"},{"time":352571,"text":"there are positive feedbacks which can be of many times,"},{"time":356168,"text":"such that previous growths enhance,"},{"time":359867,"text":"push forward, increase the next growth"},{"time":363355,"text":"through this kind of super-exponential growth,"},{"time":365857,"text":"which is very trenchant, not sustainable."},{"time":368971,"text":"And the key idea is that the mathematical solution"},{"time":372028,"text":"of this class of models exhibit finite-time singularities,"},{"time":375666,"text":"which means that there is a critical time"},{"time":379019,"text":"where the system will break, will change regime."},{"time":382223,"text":"It may be a crash. It may be just a plateau, something else."},{"time":385499,"text":"And the key idea is that the critical time,"},{"time":387766,"text":"the information about the critical time is contained"},{"time":390295,"text":"in the early development of this super-exponential growth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":395779,"text":"We have applied this theory early on, that was our first success,"},{"time":400139,"text":"to the diagnostic of the rupture of key elements"},{"time":403698,"text":"on the iron rocket."},{"time":406227,"text":"Using acoustic emission, you know, this little noise"},{"time":409049,"text":"that you hear a structure emit, sing to you"},{"time":411346,"text":"when they are stressed, and reveal the damage going on,"},{"time":415037,"text":"there's a collective phenomenon of positive feedback,"},{"time":417477,"text":"the more damage gives the more damage,"},{"time":419174,"text":"so you can actually predict,"},{"time":421649,"text":"within, of course, a probability band,"},{"time":423789,"text":"when the rupture will occur."},{"time":425702,"text":"So this is now so successful that it is used"},{"time":428137,"text":"in the initial phase of [unclear] the flight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":432502,"text":"Perhaps more surprisingly, the same type of theory"},{"time":435309,"text":"applies to biology and medicine,"},{"time":438037,"text":"parturition, the act of giving birth, epileptic seizures."},{"time":441733,"text":"From seven months of pregnancy, a mother"},{"time":445357,"text":"starts to feel episodic precursory contractions of the uterus"},{"time":451021,"text":"that are the sign of these maturations"},{"time":455125,"text":"toward the instability, giving birth to the baby,"},{"time":458549,"text":"the dragon-king."},{"time":460920,"text":"So if you measure the precursor signal,"},{"time":463526,"text":"you can actually identify pre- and post-maturity problems"},{"time":469751,"text":"in advance."},{"time":471222,"text":"Epileptic seizures also come in a large variety of size,"},{"time":474982,"text":"and when the brain goes to a super-critical state,"},{"time":478262,"text":"you have dragon-kings which have a degree of predictability"},{"time":481835,"text":"and this can help the patient to deal with this illness."},{"time":487342,"text":"We have applied this theory to many systems,"},{"time":489527,"text":"landslides, glacier collapse,"},{"time":492382,"text":"even to the dynamics of prediction of success:"},{"time":495949,"text":"blockbusters, YouTube videos, movies, and so on."},{"time":500335,"text":"But perhaps the most important application"},{"time":503471,"text":"is for finance, and this theory"},{"time":505837,"text":"illuminates, I believe, the deep reason"},{"time":509276,"text":"for the financial crisis that we have gone through."},{"time":511972,"text":"This is rooted in 30 years of history of bubbles,"},{"time":516020,"text":"starting in 1980, with the global bubble"},{"time":519732,"text":"crashing in 1987,"},{"time":521819,"text":"followed by many other bubbles."},{"time":524188,"text":"The biggest one was the \"new economy\" Internet bubble"},{"time":526900,"text":"in 2000, crashing in 2000,"},{"time":528825,"text":"the real estate bubbles in many countries,"},{"time":530873,"text":"financial derivative bubbles everywhere,"},{"time":533653,"text":"stock market bubbles also everywhere,"},{"time":535942,"text":"commodity and all bubbles, debt and credit bubbles --"},{"time":539893,"text":"bubbles, bubbles, bubbles."}]},{"cues":[{"time":542606,"text":"We had a global bubble."},{"time":545245,"text":"This is a measure of global overvaluation"},{"time":549486,"text":"of all markets, expressing what I call"},{"time":553508,"text":"an illusion of a perpetual money machine"},{"time":556677,"text":"that suddenly broke in 2007."}]},{"cues":[{"time":560629,"text":"The problem is that we see the same process,"},{"time":564863,"text":"in particular through quantitative easing,"},{"time":567594,"text":"of a thinking of a perpetual money machine nowadays"},{"time":570778,"text":"to tackle the crisis since 2008 in the U.S., in Europe,"},{"time":575181,"text":"in Japan."},{"time":577469,"text":"This has very important implications"},{"time":579859,"text":"to understand the failure of quantitative easing"},{"time":583937,"text":"as well as austerity measures"},{"time":585813,"text":"as long as we don't attack the core,"},{"time":588622,"text":"the structural cause of this perpetual money machine thinking."}]},{"cues":[{"time":593813,"text":"Now, these are big claims."},{"time":596429,"text":"Why would you believe me?"},{"time":599311,"text":"Well, perhaps because, in the last 15 years"},{"time":602191,"text":"we have come out of our ivory tower,"},{"time":605383,"text":"and started to publish ex ante --"},{"time":608119,"text":"and I stress the term ex ante, it means \"in advance\" —"},{"time":611447,"text":"before the crash confirmed"},{"time":613585,"text":"the existence of the bubble or the financial excesses."},{"time":616271,"text":"These are a few of the major bubbles"},{"time":619993,"text":"that we have lived through in recent history."},{"time":624471,"text":"Again, many interesting stories for each of them."},{"time":627311,"text":"Let me tell you just one or two stories"},{"time":630025,"text":"that deal with massive bubbles."}]},{"cues":[{"time":632071,"text":"We all know the Chinese miracle."},{"time":634407,"text":"This is the expression of the stock market"},{"time":637477,"text":"of a massive bubble, a factor of three,"},{"time":640357,"text":"300 percent in just a few years."},{"time":642527,"text":"In September 2007,"},{"time":645729,"text":"I was invited as a keynote speaker of a macro hedge fund"},{"time":649376,"text":"management conference,"},{"time":651825,"text":"and I showed to the conference a prediction"},{"time":655880,"text":"that by the end of 2007, this bubble"},{"time":660073,"text":"would change regime."},{"time":662042,"text":"There might be a crash. Certainly not sustainable."},{"time":665127,"text":"Now, how do you believe the very smart,"},{"time":670369,"text":"very motivated, very informed macro hedge fund managers"},{"time":675799,"text":"reacted to this prediction?"},{"time":677755,"text":"You know, they had made billions"},{"time":679711,"text":"just surfing this bubble until now."},{"time":682546,"text":"They told me, \"Didier,"},{"time":684130,"text":"yeah, the market might be overvalued,"},{"time":687167,"text":"but you forget something."},{"time":689063,"text":"There is the Beijing Olympic Games coming"},{"time":691415,"text":"in August 2008, and it's very clear that"},{"time":693679,"text":"the Chinese government is controlling the economy"},{"time":696871,"text":"and doing what it takes"},{"time":698224,"text":"to also avoid any wave and control the stock market.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":702671,"text":"Three weeks after my presentation,"},{"time":705142,"text":"the markets lost 20 percent"},{"time":707268,"text":"and went through a phase of volatility,"},{"time":709529,"text":"upheaval, and a total market loss of"},{"time":712255,"text":"70 percent until the end of the year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":714523,"text":"So how can we be so collectively wrong"},{"time":717399,"text":"by misreading or ignoring the science"},{"time":721541,"text":"of the fact that when an instability has developed,"},{"time":724372,"text":"and the system is ripe, any perturbation"},{"time":726823,"text":"makes it essentially impossible to control?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":730504,"text":"The Chinese market collapsed, but it rebounded."},{"time":735209,"text":"In 2009, we also identified that this new bubble,"},{"time":739965,"text":"a smaller one, was unsustainable,"},{"time":742551,"text":"so we published again a prediction, in advance,"},{"time":746183,"text":"stating that by August 2009, the market will correct,"},{"time":750510,"text":"will not continue on this track."},{"time":753191,"text":"Our critics, reading the prediction,"},{"time":756343,"text":"said, \"No, it's not possible."},{"time":760256,"text":"The Chinese government is there."},{"time":761750,"text":"They have learned their lesson. They will control."},{"time":764432,"text":"They want to benefit from the growth.\""},{"time":766239,"text":"Perhaps these critics have not learned their lesson previously."},{"time":769895,"text":"So the crisis did occur. The market corrected."}]},{"cues":[{"time":773727,"text":"The same critics then said, \"Ah, yes,"},{"time":776063,"text":"but you published your prediction."},{"time":777912,"text":"You influenced the market."},{"time":779568,"text":"It was not a prediction.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":782701,"text":"Maybe I am very powerful then."},{"time":786058,"text":"Now, this is interesting."},{"time":788102,"text":"It shows that it's essentially impossible until now"},{"time":791039,"text":"to develop a science of economics"},{"time":793167,"text":"because we are sentient beings who anticipate"},{"time":796310,"text":"and there is a problem of self-fulfilling prophesies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":800373,"text":"So we invented a new way of doing science."},{"time":804106,"text":"We created the Financial Bubble Experiment."},{"time":806818,"text":"The idea is the following. We monitor the markets."},{"time":809490,"text":"We identify excesses, bubbles."},{"time":813658,"text":"We do our work. We write a report"},{"time":816962,"text":"in which we put our prediction of the critical time."},{"time":821234,"text":"We don't release the report. It's kept secret."},{"time":823809,"text":"But with modern encrypting techniques,"},{"time":826674,"text":"we have a hash, we publish a public key,"},{"time":830696,"text":"and six months later, we release the report,"},{"time":834651,"text":"and there is authentication."},{"time":837050,"text":"And all this is done on an international archive"},{"time":841818,"text":"so that we cannot be accused of just releasing the successes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":846018,"text":"Let me tease you with a very recent analysis."},{"time":849410,"text":"17th of May, 2013, just two weeks ago,"},{"time":852668,"text":"we identified that the U.S. stock market"},{"time":854346,"text":"was on an unsustainable path"},{"time":856738,"text":"and we released this on our website on the 21st of May"},{"time":860540,"text":"that there will be a change of regime."},{"time":862585,"text":"The next day, the market started to change regime, course."},{"time":867369,"text":"This is not a crash."},{"time":868860,"text":"This is just the third or fourth act"},{"time":871459,"text":"of a massive bubble in the making."},{"time":874322,"text":"Scaling up the discussion at the size of the planet,"},{"time":877418,"text":"we see the same thing."},{"time":878443,"text":"Wherever we look, it's observable:"},{"time":881364,"text":"in the biosphere, in the atmosphere, in the ocean,"},{"time":884594,"text":"showing these super-exponential trajectories"},{"time":888498,"text":"characterizing an unsustainable path"},{"time":891129,"text":"and announcing a phase transition."},{"time":893746,"text":"This diagram on the right"},{"time":895450,"text":"shows a very beautiful compilation of studies"},{"time":898450,"text":"suggesting indeed that there is a nonlinear -- possibility"},{"time":902160,"text":"for a nonlinear transition just in the next few decades."}]},{"cues":[{"time":906309,"text":"So there are bubbles everywhere."},{"time":909931,"text":"From one side, this is exciting"},{"time":911895,"text":"for me, as a professor who chases bubbles"},{"time":914655,"text":"and slays dragons, as the media has sometimes called me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":919413,"text":"But can we really slay the dragons?"},{"time":922464,"text":"Very recently, with collaborators,"},{"time":924608,"text":"we studied a dynamical system"},{"time":927311,"text":"where you see the dragon-king as these big loops"},{"time":930215,"text":"and we were able to apply tiny perturbations at the right times"},{"time":934136,"text":"that removed, when control is on, these dragons."}]},{"cues":[{"time":939071,"text":"\"Gouverner, c'est prévoir.\""},{"time":942005,"text":"Governing is the art of planning and predicting."},{"time":947799,"text":"But is it not the case that this is probably"},{"time":950552,"text":"one of the biggest gaps of mankind,"},{"time":954452,"text":"which has the responsibility to steer"},{"time":957712,"text":"our societies and our planet toward sustainability"},{"time":960428,"text":"in the face of growing challenges and crises?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":965272,"text":"But the dragon-king theory gives hope."},{"time":969767,"text":"We learn that most systems have pockets of predictability."},{"time":973335,"text":"It is possible to develop advance diagnostics of crises"},{"time":978235,"text":"so that we can be prepared, we can take measures,"},{"time":981794,"text":"we can take responsibility,"},{"time":984549,"text":"and so that never again will"},{"time":987296,"text":"extremes and crises like the Great Recession"},{"time":991150,"text":"or the European crisis take us by surprise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":995560,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":997035,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}